title: Obscure and from 1571...
content:
If you wanted find a better image of “Ordre tenu au sacre de Princesse Elisabeth d’ Autriche”. than what is in Morrison’s “Four Centuries of fine Printing”, page 128; where would you look? It was published in Paris 1571.
